{"tid":2239773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"AO港台副處長馮建業指「無罪假定」再查利君雅 梁家榮斥馮用字不當","createTime":"2020-10-12T08:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T10:48:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"66f4f262bf6c72bf81c7452324369dbee8f44221","tid":2239773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"香港電台《視點31》主持利君雅上月底被延長試用期120日，並重啟有關投訴她的調查。港台節目製作人員工會今午召開員工大會，要求管方交代重啟調查的理據，「是否所有需要通過試用期的同事都被重新審視表現，還是今次是對人不對事？」<br />\n<br />\n員工大會今午在港台舉行，廣播處長梁家榮、負責處理重啟調查一事的副處長兼政務官馮建業，數十名包括新聞部和電視部等員工均有出席。消息指，馮建業在會上以「無罪假定」來解釋重啟調查利君雅的決定，遭梁家榮在席間反批「用字不當」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=f62df94c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FPX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU%2F&h=ff4fb650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/PX3JQSPK2BHCLGSWDKZ5PDITAU/</a>"},{"pid":"0fbffab7f87b616c393d3c9388a4257bcef58c70","tid":2239773,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f1e73be110b2c5d831f8aa03928492dbc0719b","tid":2239773,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fbffab7f87b616c393d3c9388a4257bcef58c70","tid":2239773,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/